Compare {{cog|stq|soaltich|t=salty}}, {{cog|fy|sâltich|t=salty}}, {{cog|nl|zoutig|t=salty}}, {{cog|nds-de|soltig|t=salty}}, {{cog|de|salzig|t=salty}}.

